Package: radafruitio
Type: Package
Title: An Interface to the Adafruit IO API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Ernest", family = "Guevarra",
    email = "ernest@guevarra.io", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4887-4415"))
Description: Adafruit IO is a platform designed by Adafruit to display, respond, 
    and interact with any internet of things (IoT) project's data. The Adafruit 
    IO HTTP API provides access to Adafruit IO data from any programming 
    language or hardware environment that can speak HTTP. The radafruitio
    package provides functions to interface with the Adafruit IO HTTP API
    through R.
